### Create a new inventory item
POST http://localhost:8080/admin/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Bun",
  "type": "INGREDIENT",
  "uom": "pcs",
  "decimals": 0,
  "lowStockThreshold": 25,
  "initialOnHand": 100
}

### Update an inventory item
PATCH http://localhost:8080/admin/items/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "lowStockThreshold": 50
}

### Manual adjustment (subtract 5 units)
POST http://localhost:8080/admin/items/1/adjust
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "delta": -5,
  "reason": "MANUAL",
  "note": "Used for catering order"
}

### Sync Square catalog variations
POST http://localhost:8080/admin/catalog/sync

### Define a recipe component
POST http://localhost:8080/admin/recipes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "variationId": "VARIATION_BURGER_STD",
  "inventoryItemId": 1,
  "qtyPerSale": 2,
  "modifierCatalogObjectId": ""
}

### Inspect recipe components for a variation
GET http://localhost:8080/admin/recipes/VARIATION_BURGER_STD

### Get low stock items
GET http://localhost:8080/admin/low-stock

### Paginated ledger (first 20 entries)
GET http://localhost:8080/admin/ledger?limit=20&offset=0

### Simulated webhook call (development only)
### NOTE: In dev you can set ALLOW_UNVERIFIED_WEBHOOKS=true to skip signature checks
POST http://localhost:8080/webhooks/square
Content-Type: application/json
X-Square-Hmacsha256-Signature: REPLACE_IN_PROD

{
  "event_id": "evt-sample-payment-1",
  "type": "payment.updated",
  "data": {
    "object": {
      "payment": {
        "id": "PAYMENT_ID_FROM_SQUARE",
        "status": "COMPLETED",
        "orderId": "ORDER_ID_FROM_SQUARE"
      }
    }
  }
}
